name: The Deadly Own goal
description:
This illustration is the moment, of the deadly own goal. in the soccer match at the 1994 fifa world cup usa, between colombia vs usa. which was accidentally made by andres escobar. andres escobar was a colombian fotballer.
andres war murdered in the aftermath, of the 1994 fifa world cup. andres was killed by, the cartel who placed huge bets on the national team, and obviously lost.
